0.10.0 (03 Feb 2018)
--------------------
* Feature added: Calendar mode.
* Layout adapted to tablets.
* User interface bug fix.
* Data export suggested file name fix.

0.9.1 (10 Dec 2017)
-------------------
* Notifications issue fix.

0.9.0 (25 Sep 2017)
-------------------
* Layout redesigned.
* Time zones added to the tasks.
* Week day displayed.
* Data export/import improved and simplified. CSV format removed.
* German language added.
* Bug when deleting the current context fixed.

0.8.0 (27 Oct 2016)
-------------------
* User interface improved.
* Data bug fix.
* Bug fix on task counting by tag.
* Spanish language bug fix.

0.7.1 (25 Jan 2016)
-------------------
* Reminders bug fix.

0.7.0 (16 Jan 2016)
-------------------
* Task description edition improved.
* Reminders bug fix.

0.6.0 (25 Dec 2015)
-------------------
* CSV format added for data exporting.
* Reminders bug fixes.
* Tag filtering bug fix.

0.5.0 (16 Dec 2015)
-------------------
* Date concept improved:
  - Single date added.
  - Time can optionally be added to dates.
  - Dates/times are shown in the device local timezone.
* Feature added: reminders.
* Task sorting improved.
* Tags sorted alphabetically.
* Tag filtering improved.
* User interface bug fixes.
* Internal settings bug fix.
* Spanish language bug fix.

0.4.0 (08 Jul 2015)
-------------------
* Feature added: data export and import.

0.3.0 (15 Apr 2015)
-------------------
* Feature added: context edition.

